Create and Share Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management App

Create an app from the Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management template.

To create the app, go to CRM Analytics Studio. Click Create. Select App | Create App from Template, and then open the template picker. Select Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management, and then click Continue.

If the instance's compatibility check fails, add the required data, and then create the app again. Enter a name for your app, and then click Create.

After the process is completed, to see your app, refresh the page. If you see an error message that the Analytics Integration User doesnâ€™t have access to selected fields, edit Salesforce field-level security.

To share the app with your users, in CRM Analytics Studio, open your app. You can share the app only with users who have the relevant admin or user permission set. On the Give Access tab of the share window, under Invite others, add the names of users that you want to share the app with.
title: Creating and Sharing Subscriber Lifecycle Management Apps
